snippet.title: The Adventure of Ninomae Ina'nis - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Adventure of Ninomae Ina'nis is a vertical shoot 'em up game where you control Ninomae Ina'nis from Hololive Myth and her companion AO-chan.

The Takodachi have gone missing and it is up to Ina and AO-chan to find them!

Available on Steam September 12th - 2024!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3143980/The_Adventure_of_Ninomae_Inanis/
